        {
            "title": "TD Cowen生成式AI採用調查看好這些股票",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - TD <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Cowen\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Cowen;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Cowen\">Cowen</a>分析師Derrick Wood主導的一項最新調查報告顯示,人工智能貨幣化正接近拐點,現有軟體供應商的受益程度將超過市場目前的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司針對生產力套件市場發布的第三份報告,基於對689名美國採購決策者的調查,發現生成式AI的採用已相當普遍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Wood表示,92%的受訪者至少使用三大供應商之一,包括微軟Copilot(70%)、谷歌Gemini(55%)和OpenAI的ChatGPT(53%),而企業平均部署2.6家AI代理供應商。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2967d639-5a63-3203-998b-b4ad246e41f1-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管採用率很高,但貨幣化程度仍然較低。不過TD Cowen預計這種情況將會改變,75%的受訪者表示AI代理帶來了正面的投資回報率,79%的<span><span><span><span>微軟</span></span></span></span> 365用戶和80%的Google Workspace用戶表示,他們在未來12至18個月內有些可能或非常可能升級其套件訂閱。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告對企業SaaS供應商特別看好。Wood寫道,這些數據「描繪出比目前股價所反映的更有利的AI貨幣化前景,尤其是對企業SaaS供應商而言。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">TD Cowen指出Salesforce、ServiceNow和SAP為主要受益者,並指出儘管橫向AI代理目前採用率最低,但其感知投資回報率最高,58%的用戶表示獲得3倍或更高的回報。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">自主AI的採用也將大幅加速,TD Cowen預計部署率將從目前的34%增加一倍以上,到2027年下半年達到77%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">具體針對微軟,TD Cowen將其Microsoft 365商業收入的複合年增長率預測從約13.5%上調至15%(至2030財年),目前預計收入將達到1,056億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/td-cowen%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E5%BC%8Fai%E6%8E%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E9%80%99%E4%BA%9B%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8-155115726.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-25 00:02:48",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "貝萊德全球首席投資策略師稱在人工智能熱潮中看好半導體和硬體股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 貝萊德全球首席投資策略師Wei Li表示，作為<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"人工智能\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>戰略的一部分，該資產管理公司增持了半導體和硬體股票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Li周五表示，人工智能行業目前正處於發展階段，最終是模型提供商、計算提供商，還是擁有強大數據和智慧財產權的公司將占據主導地位，目前尚不清楚。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「就應用階段而言，我認為目前還沒有定論，」她在採訪中對彭博電視表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Li以無需接入電網的表後發電為例，指出能源生產技術的進步使企業能夠增加資本支出。再加上科技股估值已「回歸」至與整體市場一致的水平，這些發展趨勢支持了貝萊德對人工智能和美股的超配立場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-87f454aa-5f95-3876-88ac-a0aa3054aeb6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"貝萊德首席全球投資策略師Wei Li探討了人工智能股票、資本支出和盈利前景來源：彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/TbooUwpI5hqIeORyCjH2uA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/103cb9d816a23dbb6614fad57a016e24\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">貝萊德首席全球投資策略師Wei Li探討了人工智能股票、資本支出和盈利前景來源：彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她表示，儘管中東戰爭推高了油氣價格，尤其是在歐洲和亞太地區，但風險資產仍展現出驚人的韌性。美國股市上漲了中個位數，Li認為這得益於美國相對較高的能源獨立性和維持良好的信用利差。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Li指出，儘管伊朗衝突可能導致全球GDP下降0.2%至0.3%，但歐洲和亞洲受到的影響可能比美國更大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BlackRock’s Li Favors Semis, Hardware in AI Investment Push</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E5%B8%AB%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%86%B1%E6%BD%AE%E4%B8%AD%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E5%92%8C%E7%A1%AC%E9%AB%94%E8%82%A1-151344434.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 23:55:10",
