        {
            "title": "DA Davidson上調AMD評級,稱CPU需求進入「前所未有」階段",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6_CrUd2j8qGyL_GQv5r0.g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA7I0CN_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - DA Davidson週五上調了Advanced Micro Devices (<span><span><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"AMD\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:AMD;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/AMD\">AMD</a></span></span>)的評級,將評級從中性上調至買入,並將目標價從220美元上調至375美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Gil Luria指出他們所稱的「CPU需求結構性增長」,以及AMD在加速數據中心建設中所扮演角色的可見度提升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DA Davidson表示,現在預期「AMD的預估將出現顯著上調,從3月季度開始」,該公司將於5月5日公布財報。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-72c6ce7f-539f-3596-8fe3-9d55cccc93e2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司還指出,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"英特爾\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:英特爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英特爾\">英特爾</a>超預期的業績是CPU市場重新加速的關鍵信號。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據該報告,「英特爾的業績顯示(它)已經轉化為非常顯著的上行空間」,高管們強調到2027年行業將實現兩位數增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師認為,隨著代理工作負載將計算需求從GPU轉移,CPU正在「重新確立自己作為AI時代不可或缺基礎的地位」。他們引用英特爾的觀點,即GPU與CPU的比率,曾經在預訓練時約為8比1,現在「在代理工作負載中正接近平價」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">DA Davidson稱英特爾的表現預示著AMD的CPU業務將實現巨大飛躍,認為向代理AI工作負載的轉變正在為服務器CPU創造前所未有的需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司補充說,隨著需求可能超過供應,AMD處於有利位置,可以在整個產品組合中提高價格。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師將2026年營收預估上調20億美元,毛利潤上調15億美元,稱最近的數據使AMD的長期目標「更容易實現」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/da-davidson%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BFamd%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A-%E7%A8%B1cpu%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E9%80%B2%E5%85%A5-%E5%89%8D%E6%89%80%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89-%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5-140453886.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 22:55:07",
